Package com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.dao

Class HeroDAOImpl

java.lang.Object
com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.dao.HeroDAOImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
HeroDAO
@Repository public class HeroDAOImpl extends Object implements HeroDAO
Implementation of the HeroDAO interface for managing operations related to Heroes using JDBC. This class provides the logic for the CRUD operations on the Hero entity in the database.
